Class ZingleAttachmentService

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.zingle.api.sdk.services.ZingleBaseService<ZingleAttachment>
      • me.zingle.api.sdk.services.ZingleAttachmentService

  • public class ZingleAttachmentService
extends ZingleBaseService<ZingleAttachment>
    ZingleBaseService derivation for working with ZingleAttachment. Class haven't any reflection in API, so doesn't implement any API functions. Serves as helper class for parsing and handling ZingleMessage attachments.
